# Lipi — Cursor IDE rules
# Auto-loaded by Cursor IDE for every chat in this project.
# Full source of truth: docs/ENGINEERING.md, AGENTS.md, HANDOFF.md.

## Workspace
- Project: Lipi (a cross-platform Cursor-like IDE, Tauri 2 + React 18 + TS + Vite + Monaco)
- Root: C:\Users\Pv Vimal Nair\lipi\
- Sibling project (DO NOT TOUCH): C:\Users\Pv Vimal Nair\lifeof\ (Flutter)
